595
00:27:28,357 --> 00:27:29,636
I tell her? Or you?

596
00:27:29,637 --> 00:27:31,047
I'll tell her.

597
00:27:47,676 --> 00:27:48,607
Aunty.

598
00:27:49,797 --> 00:27:50,596
