607
00:28:05,837 --> 00:28:07,647
you should do at home.

608
00:28:07,716 --> 00:28:09,246
Actually,

609
00:28:09,317 --> 00:28:10,356
there's laundry instruction

610
00:28:10,357 --> 00:28:12,087
labelled on the clothes.

611
00:28:12,196 --> 00:28:13,887
You can check on it
before doing the laundry.

612
00:28:13,916 --> 00:28:15,726
The clothes that need to be dry-cleaned
can be sent to the laundry.

613
00:28:15,877 --> 00:28:17,076
I've also listed

614
00:28:17,077 --> 00:28:19,047
the schedule for changing
bedsheets and blanket covers,

615
00:28:19,716 --> 00:28:23,235
and the routine of Cong and Qi for you.

616
00:28:23,236 --> 00:28:24,887
You can read it when you have time.

617
00:28:34,676 --> 00:28:36,876
And, if there are things

618
00:28:36,877 --> 00:28:37,995
I don't need you to handle,

619
00:28:37,996 --> 00:28:40,807
