664
00:30:49,037 --> 00:30:49,926
Aunty,

665
00:30:50,476 --> 00:30:51,486
I think

666
00:30:51,597 --> 00:30:53,526
there's one thing I have to tell you,

667
00:30:56,196 --> 00:30:56,836
Cong and Qi

668
00:30:56,837 --> 00:30:58,726
are actually not my child.

669
00:31:00,037 --> 00:31:01,755
