686
00:33:22,716 --> 00:33:23,726
Come in.

687
00:33:40,797 --> 00:33:41,475
Oh my god!

688
00:33:41,476 --> 00:33:43,607
This cat is so cute.

689
00:33:45,157 --> 00:33:46,847
What is its name?

690
00:33:47,357 --> 00:33:48,407
Its name is Goldie.

691
00:33:48,756 --> 00:33:50,556
Goldie, nice to meet you.

692
00:33:50,557 --> 00:33:51,766
Goldie.

693
00:33:53,196 --> 00:33:54,915
Your cousin lives
a passionate life, huh?

694
00:33:54,916 --> 00:33:56,486
He has so many plants.

695
00:33:58,317 --> 00:33:59,807
