704
00:34:15,157 --> 00:34:16,847
I haven't decided where to go yet.

705
00:34:17,676 --> 00:34:19,407
I give myself a month to figure it out.

706
00:34:19,917 --> 00:34:21,207
Maybe back to Shanghai,

707
00:34:21,437 --> 00:34:23,086
or somewhere else.

708
00:34:26,157 --> 00:34:27,327
I don't know yet

709
00:34:27,477 --> 00:34:28,887
the exact place I will go.

710
00:34:29,037 --> 00:34:30,606
The thing is,

711
00:34:31,517 --> 00:34:33,847
I'm not sure who I'll meet.

712
00:34:51,196 --> 00:34:53,086
So, the person you meet

713
00:34:54,637 --> 00:34:56,367
