717
00:35:15,196 --> 00:35:15,675
Yes.

718
00:35:15,676 --> 00:35:16,887
I'll feed them some.

719
00:35:17,316 --> 00:35:19,167
Let me give you some snacks.

720
00:35:19,196 --> 00:35:20,566
Don't run away.

721
00:35:21,276 --> 00:35:21,956
Alright.

722
00:35:21,957 --> 00:35:22,966
Thank you.

723
00:35:25,756 --> 00:35:26,956
Look at you,

724
00:35:26,957 --> 00:35:28,006
little glutton.

725
00:35:34,037 --> 00:35:35,367
Is it okay to sit on the floor?

726
00:35:35,676 --> 00:35:36,727
Yes.

727
00:35:36,796 --> 00:35:39,367
We just have this coffee table to eat at.

728
00:35:39,716 --> 00:35:40,687
That's fine.

729
00:35:41,316 --> 00:35:42,646
Stop cooking more.

730
00:35:43,196 --> 00:35:44,367
Just one more dish.

731
00:35:46,037 --> 00:35:46,887
