737
00:36:09,117 --> 00:36:10,207
A soft drink, please.

738
00:36:14,836 --> 00:36:16,006
Nice to meet you.

739
00:36:17,477 --> 00:36:18,926
You're funny.

740
00:36:20,637 --> 00:36:21,795
A bit too formal?

741
00:36:21,796 --> 00:36:23,086
