742
00:36:23,236 --> 00:36:26,167
Welcome to my place.

743
00:36:27,157 --> 00:36:28,156
Thank you, chef.

744
00:36:28,157 --> 00:36:29,086
You've worked hard.

745
00:36:35,997 --> 00:36:37,247
Shall we dig in now?

746
00:36:37,276 --> 00:36:38,207
Yes.

747
00:36:59,557 --> 00:37:00,847
This is really delicious.

748
00:37:01,517 --> 00:37:03,715
