enjoy what you like.

762
00:37:26,957 --> 00:37:29,807
No need to care what people think.

763
00:37:31,077 --> 00:37:32,606
I think you're right.

764
00:37:33,037 --> 00:37:33,916
Everyone around me

765
00:37:33,917 --> 00:37:35,926
