766
00:37:36,437 --> 00:37:38,675
scroll through short videos,

767
00:37:38,676 --> 00:37:40,526
go to karaoke, or have some barbecue.

768
00:37:40,637 --> 00:37:42,596
If you live a different way,

769
00:37:42,597 --> 00:37:44,006
they think you're being pretentious.

770
00:37:46,157 --> 00:37:47,086
So,

771
00:37:47,316 --> 00:37:48,315
do you think

772
00:37:48,316 --> 00:37:49,767
you're a pretentious person?

773
00:37:50,157 --> 00:37:51,327
What do you think?

774
00:37:56,037 --> 00:37:56,715
Like you said,

775
00:37:56,716 --> 00:37:58,687
