the day after tomorrow.

800
00:39:53,356 --> 00:39:55,727
I'll come with you by the time.

801
00:39:58,117 --> 00:39:59,006
No need.

802
00:39:59,356 --> 00:40:00,596
You can make your own plans.

803
00:40:00,597 --> 00:40:01,566
I'll be fine.

804
00:40:02,637 --> 00:40:03,486
That's okay.

805
00:40:03,557 --> 00:40:05,167
I don't have much else going on.

806
00:40:06,597 --> 00:40:07,966
I'll go in first.

807
00:40:15,316 --> 00:40:16,446
